videos.description: Defensive lineman Freddie Booth-Lloyd makes up for costing the Owls a 5-yard penalty by dropping and giving the coaches ten on the sideline.
videos.headline: Temple lineman pays for penalties with push-ups

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Temple lineman pays for penalties with push-ups) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: Black Knights RB Darnell Woolfolk stays on his feet after being swarmed by Temple defenders and gets into the end zone in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Army rushes 11 yards for first TD

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army rushes 11 yards for first TD) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: The Black Knights capitalize on a 24-yard gain with a successful 4-yard rushing touchdown for RB Darnell Woolfolk.
videos.headline: Woolfolk scores second consecutive TD for Army

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Woolfolk scores second consecutive TD for Army) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: Owls WR Isaiah Wright fends off Army defenders with stiff-arms and zippy speed to score for Temple.
videos.headline: Wright's 50-yard TD run puts Temple on the board

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wright's 50-yard TD run puts Temple on the board) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: The Owls tie it with the Black Knights at 14 after QB Frank Nutile lobs a 37 yard pass over the middle to connect with WR Adonis Jennings in the end zone.
videos.headline: Temple executes flawless 30-yard TD strike

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Temple executes flawless 30-yard TD strike) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: The Owls lead the Black Knights 21-14 in the fourth quarter after RB Ryquell Armstead breezes past the Army defense to score.
videos.headline: Temple reclaims lead with 43-yard run

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Temple reclaims lead with 43-yard run) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: Army RB Darnell Woolfolk completes the hat trick as he breaks free for a 44-yard TD run, tying Temple at 21 in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Woolfolk racks up 3rd TD for Army

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Woolfolk racks up 3rd TD for Army) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: RB Ryquell Armstead leaves a trail of Army defenders behind and strides up the sideline 21 yards for a late 28-21 lead over Army in the fourth quarter
videos.headline: Temple's Armstead explodes up the field to take back lead

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Temple's Armstead explodes up the field to take back lead) 2017/10/21 ESHEET

videos.description: Black Knights QB Kelvin Hopkins hits WR Jermaine Adams with a 16-yard back shoulder fade in the final six seconds to tie Temple at 28.
videos.headline: Army makes incredible TD grab to ensure OT

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army makes incredible TD grab to ensure OT) 2017/10/21 ESHEET
